# Log Analyzer Web App (Cybersecurity Project)

This is a Flask-based web application that analyzes log files to detect suspicious activity.

## Features
- Upload log files
- Detect most active users and IPs
- Identify suspicious users
- Count errors (HTTP 4xx, 5xx)

## Tech Used
- Python
- Flask

## How to Run
1. Install Flask: pip install flask
2. Run: python app.py
3. Open: http://127.0.0.1:5000/

## Use Case
Helps identify potential security threats from log data.